API 的行为就像您没有向其发送 API 密钥的值一样。
查看是否属实：
URI url = new URI(API_URL);
HttpURLConnection connection = (HttpURLConnection)
url.toURL().openConnection();

// 验证 API_KEY
if (API_KEY == null || API_KEY.isEmpty() || !API_KEY.startsWith(&quot;sk-&quot;)) {
System.out.println(&quot;无效 API_KEY: &quot; + API_KEY);
throw new IllegalArgumentException(&quot;API_KEY 无效或设置不正确。&quot;);
}

// 将请求方法设置为 POST
connection.setRequestMethod(&quot;POST&quot;);
connection.setRequestProperty(&quot;Content-Type&quot;, &quot;application/json;charset=utf-8&quot;);
connection.setRequestProperty(&quot;Authorization&quot;, &quot;Bearer &quot; + API_KEY);
connection.setDoOutput(true);

// 发送请求
